       gram which expects bug reports to conform to a standard format.	 _S_e_n_d_-
       _b_u_g  is a shell script to help the user compose and mail	bug reports in
       the correct format.  _S_e_n_d_b_u_g works by invoking the editor specified  by
       the  environment	 variable _E_D_I_T_O_R on a temporary	copy of	the bug	report
